verbose_text: However, the potential correlation between vascular ECs autophagy was not discussed intensively, although we have demonstrated the vital effect of ECs autophagy on increasing EC migration and proliferation, which coincided with the in vivo experimental results that the application of Cur, as a type of antioxidant and antiproliferative agent, accelerated reendothelialization and suppressed IH.
